author: PlayStation
description:
The climb of a lifetime starts on January 29, 2026! Play the demo or add Cairn to your wishlist: https://bit.ly/Cairn-PS5Store

Set out to conquer the legendary Mount Kami. Find your route, uncover lost history, and survive the ascent. Every encounter and discovery will test your resolve.

Cairn features realistic simulation that allows you to climb intuitively, anywhere. Find the best holds and place your hands and feet seamlessly with simple controls. Adapt your posture, effort and balance - if you're not careful, you will fall!

The demo is available on PS5 right now to keep you busy until the launch. In Cairn's demo you attempt your first ascent before heading to mount Kami. After a warm-up in the climbing gym, you climb to the summit of Mount Tenzen. You have full freedom to explore the small mountain ridge, forage, bivouac, and improve your technique in a low-pressure environment.

#ps5 #ps5games
title: Cairn - Launch Date Trailer | PS5 Games

description:
Paint the stars with the blood of your enemies in this Samurai Space Opera, Action RPG set in an alt-future solar system ruled by the sword. A pulse-pounding soundtrack drives your gravity-defying, blood-soaked path of revenge as Yuzuki the “Shattered Heir” to a massacred clan who becomes an outlaw ronin. 

Key Features: 
Discover a Moon like you've never seen. Explore this planetary gateway to the solar system, and seat of power to the Shogunate. It's a dangerous, beautiful place to discover.

Space Samurai Combat: To be a space samurai is to master your weapons, your gear and gravity itself. Choose from multiple weapons, tech-enhanced for multi-planetary warfare and Hack and Slash your enemies. 

Transcend Flesh & Steel: Become the ultimate genetically-enhanced weapon by infusing your weapon of choice and bio-ceramic body with different elements and gene splices to customize your approach to warfare.
